description: Zayn Parker has been in quite the funk lately, and it hasn't gone unnoticed by those around him, namely roomie Scott Finn, who decides he's gonna get to the bottom of Zayn's issues. Turns out, what Zayn needs is some good sexual healing, and Scott is dead set on helping Zayn out. Zayn would've never thought Scott would make a pass at him, but it turns out Scott is only mostly straight. This is news to Zayn, who doesn't quite believe Scott's convictions, that is, until Scott takes him to the bedroom and gives him the deep dick therapy he so desperately needs. Maybe brighter days are ahead for Zayn, but for now, he's content to get his fun in when and where he can.Enjoy!
title: Sudden Temptations
